<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="8" />的煙火大會已經開始了。<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />你快看看<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來吧，<delay20 />我很期待這次會有怎樣的表演喔。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也是來看煙火的嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽著這足以撼動全身的重低音，<delay20 />
會讓人心情跟著亢奮起來呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />小時候祖母牽著我的手，<delay20 />
一起去看的那場煙火大會，<delay20 />
一直讓我無法忘懷<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道當時看見的那位<delay20 />
穿著浴衣的漂亮大姊姊，<delay20 />
現在過得好不好<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在名為夜空的畫布上，<delay20 />
巨大的花朵在盛開後隨風消散<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那瞬間的虛幻充滿了美感啊。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火也有各式各樣的種類喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管哪種顏色或形狀，都有其魅力所在，<delay20 />
真的是一秒也不能錯過呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">對了，<tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在電視劇裡<delay20 />不是會有告白時，<delay20 />
聲音被煙火蓋過的場景嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想重現一下那個情景，你聽聽看喔。<10_4 />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="150" />我從以前就很喜歡你了——！<pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="100" />怎麼樣？<delay8 />我的聲音<delay20 />
有傳達給你嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火<delay20 />真的很漂亮呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你知道有什麼<delay20 />比那更美麗嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就是高興地看著煙火的你<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所露出的笑容喔……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這種時候，<delay20 />
我就會把這景色<delay20 />
用內心的快門記錄下來。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟在這世上，<delay20 />
仍然有些樂趣是無法<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />透過照片和影片來體驗的喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再過不久，這段時間也要結束了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我<delay20 />在每發煙火發射時，<delay20 />
都會在心中許下願望呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望這座島能夠維持和平，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還有希望能跟你和睦相處喔。<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺現在這一切都能實現呢。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />越是歡樂的時光，就越是讓人希望能
永遠持續下去……<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然而正因為時間有限，<delay20 />
所以那才能成為特別的回憶啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你有好好享受煙火大會嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在<delay20 />非常地開心喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>